    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1088640/extras/e79d592116842a775afdea7343fb072d.avif?t=1716564838\" width=620 height=116 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1088640/extras/93bdc1aa7394f05b8f2bf1a6ac79f335.webp?t=1716564838\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1088640/extras/477530aadc28779e0b9aaef1d35410e0.poster.avif?t=1716564838\" width=614 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1088640/extras/477530aadc28779e0b9aaef1d35410e0.webm?t=1716564838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1088640/extras/477530aadc28779e0b9aaef1d35410e0.mp4?t=1716564838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>克拉肯部落深知大海的危险性。他们崇拜这个庞然大物，敬畏它的威力，尊重它的天生本领，并在它俯首称王时利用它的力量。 那些对残酷的大海心怀恐惧的信徒们在其充满鱼类的海岸蓬勃发展，但也深知其危险而不愿远航。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1088640/extras/91e035a6526e46c162276a1f88ae21f1.webp?t=1716564838\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1088640/extras/5eee373707fe93336f772c8b0ffe08ee.avif?t=1716564838\" width=614 height=220 /></span><br><br>她是风暴的继承人，带着海洋的愤怒。她是女武神训练的女主人，同时也是她们中最出色的。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1088640/extras/414e54b27ac1cb75b4114758229c7c05.webp?t=1716564838\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1088640/extras/7515853bd9f9351047fc73d63b2544b5.poster.avif?t=1716564838\" width=614 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1088640/extras/7515853bd9f9351047fc73d63b2544b5.webm?t=1716564838\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1088640/extras/7515853bd9f9351047fc73d63b2544b5.mp4?t=1716564838\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这个部落被注入了一种叫做怀德的黑魔法。只要怀德处于积极变动状态，克拉肯就会提供新的村民。如果无法满足这个生物，那就只有那些溺水者的灵魂会以幽灵勇士的形式加入部落。<br><br>作为命运的掌控者，只有强大的伦格巴克尔女预言家掌握了怀德的神秘力量，能够化身为凶猛的女武神。这使她们成为了部落的心脏和传统的守护者。 <br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1088640/extras/3b22a838fdbe5f14168d15e482ae2d82.avif?t=1716564838\" width=620 height=116 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1088640/extras/2efac2dff28b713e34b2af9430dc54b6.webp?t=1716564838\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>你无法建造长船码头且无法使用商业胜利，但钓鱼小屋的效果会提升，并能用于在湖里和海里钓鱼<br></li><li>在非沿海地区，殖民和建造花费更高，单位的攻击力会减少。这可以通过高潮来改变<br></li><li>祭台会取代酿酒厂，并生产怀德<br></li><li>你会获得并控制幽灵勇士。建造赫尔加尔并拥有消极的怀德能让你拥有更多幽灵勇士。<br></li><li>女预言家可以进化成女武神。</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1088640/extras/2efac2dff28b713e34b2af9430dc54b6.webp?t=1716564838\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><strong>声望200: 未来展望</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>幽灵勇士会增加其所在区域的产出<br></li><li>活动比其他部落要早开始得多。<br></li><li>每当克拉肯接近海岸时，你的部落都会大摆宴席</li></ul><br><strong>声望500: 海洋之主的咆哮</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>你能拥有的幽灵勇士上限会增加<br></li><li>阵亡的军事单位有几率加入你的幽灵勇士队伍</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1088640/extras/264c300bd948de79a839b2c6ccab6c08.webp?t=1716564838\" width=620 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1088640/extras/6b7fc6ad4a74bb4588d049794713fd25.avif?t=1716564838\" width=614 height=220 /></span><br><br>你可以强制引发克拉肯活动。<br><br>在克拉肯活动期间，如果有任何船只被摧毁，你都将获得资源。",
